// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6119 — Mass File Rename (cloak)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: f87167b9-11bc-5966-ad19-0b0e412471bf

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
